    "description": "这是一款以吸血鬼庄园为背景的轻解迷游戏，创作灵感来源于年少时期玩《恶魔城系列》游戏的经历，同时结合了对于吸血鬼文化的理解与思考。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>突然醒来后发现自已在一个陌生的庄园里，你尝试寻找离开庄园的路，却发现在同一个长廊里无限循环，似乎有某种力量在影响这一切。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>在一次又一次的循环中，你发现这里的秘密，原来是吸血鬼的造出无限循环的空间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>每次探索的时间有限，擦亮双眼尽快做出选择！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>仔细对照场景中的一切，看看是否有异常。<br></li><li>如果有异常立刻回头，如果没有异常，请一直向前走。<br></li><li>确认选择后，回到安全区点燃蜡烛<br></li><li>每次探索都有时间限制，请抓紧时间。<br></li><li></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作方式</h2>WASD - 移动<br>右键 - 放大<br>Shift - 跑步<br>键 - 收集<br>G键- 书本<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容：</h2>有三个不同的关卡，时长约为60--120分钟。",
